contents:
Title: Library of SM and anomalous WWgamma couplings for the e+e- -> f \bar{f}
  n\gamma Monte Carlo programs Abstract: A brief description of the library of the Standard Model and anomalous
WWgamma coupling contribution to the matrix element for e+e- -> \nu \bar{\nu}
n\gamma process is given. It can be used with any Monte Carlo program for e+e-
-> f \bar f n\gamma processes. A working example of the application for the
KORALZ version 4.04 is also provided.
